00:20:46.547 --> 00:20:49.150 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] This guy is an ally?

00:20:49.183 --> 00:20:51.786 position:24% line:83% align:start
A guy who would do
something so brutal.

00:20:51.819 --> 00:20:53.487 position:16% line:89% align:start
I mean who is he, really?

00:20:54.722 --> 00:20:57.357 position:35% line:83% align:start
That's it.
Yes, this is perfect!

00:20:57.390 --> 00:21:00.962 position:13% line:83% align:start
You just keep looking at me
with those pretty eyes.

00:21:00.995 --> 00:21:02.730 position:7% line:89% align:start
Don't take your eyes off of me.

00:21:02.764 --> 00:21:03.598 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gasps softly]

00:21:08.136 --> 00:21:10.303 position:24% line:83% align:start
Your safe direction
is northeast,

00:21:10.337 --> 00:21:13.241 position:21% line:83% align:start
and your lucky color
is cerulean blue.

00:21:13.273 --> 00:21:16.711 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I must inform you,
you're all out of chances.

00:21:17.545 --> 00:21:20.114 position:21% line:83% align:start
In only a few minutes
of battle,

00:21:20.148 --> 00:21:22.583 position:35% line:83% align:start
you've aged
exponentially further.

00:21:22.617 --> 00:21:24.719 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:21:31.391 --> 00:21:33.360 position:24% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:21:39.700 --> 00:21:41.602 position:24% line:83% align:start
["Distant Dreamer"
by Duffy playing]

00:23:13.961 --> 00:23:15.495 position:21% line:89% align:start
Jolyne, are you okay?

00:23:15.529 --> 00:23:19.600 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yeah, I just started
to feel a lot of pain suddenly.

00:23:19.634 --> 00:23:22.069 position:10% line:89% align:start
But we need to find them now,

00:23:22.103 --> 00:23:25.106 position:13% line:83% align:start
you know, the bone, and the
little guy that picked it up.

00:23:26.207 --> 00:23:28.142 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[groans]
-Just wait a few minutes.

00:23:28.175 --> 00:23:29.844 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna repair
your wounds now.

00:23:30.544 --> 00:23:32.647 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, but hurry!

00:23:32.680 --> 00:23:35.082 position:19% line:83% align:start
We have to get it back
and fast!

00:23:36.083 --> 00:23:37.718 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] It has Dad's disc.

00:23:39.452 --> 00:23:40.388 position:38% line:89% align:start
[beeping]

00:23:45.626 --> 00:23:47.061 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[machine rumbling]
-[beeping]

